vulns.details: In resolv_cache_lookup of res_cache.cpp, there is a possible side channel information disclosure. This could lead to local information disclosure of accessed web resources with no additional execution privileges needed. User interaction is not needed for exploitation.

In send_vc of res_send.cpp, there is a possible out of bounds read due to an incorrect bounds check. This could lead to local information disclosure with no additional execution privileges needed. User interaction is not needed for exploitation.

In run of MDnsSdListener.cpp, there is a possible memory corruption due to a use after free. This could lead to local escalation of privilege with no additional execution privileges needed. User interaction is not needed for exploitation.
